Class SolJMSErrorCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.solacesystems.jms.impl.SolJMSErrorCodes

  • public class SolJMSErrorCodes
extends Object
    This class defines the Solace specific string error codes for JMS exceptions.

      • EC_SPOOL_OVER_QUOTA_ERROR

        public static final String EC_SPOOL_OVER_QUOTA_ERROR
        The client has attempted to publish to a spool which already over quota. It may be a spool associated with a subscriber, queue, or topic endpoint. It may also be a quota problem of global or message-vpn scope and not just a single spool that can not be published to. Related JMS exception: JMSException
